{
  "stem": "15082.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Marczeniek, my dad had kept some merchandise that he had from the store, and trusted it with Marczeniek.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he had asked the SS, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Montek, whether he would like to get some-- to make himself some nice boots, some material or everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the next package that this Polish man brought there was leather for the Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Montek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And by befriending him like this, my dad's story was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at one day when he arrived at the house to clean, he said to him that on the next day, when you ascend here, you can go free, if you want.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] My dad came back to camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he quietly told some of the people, not that he's running away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But that he has a feeling that the camp will be liquidated at a near future, just giving them the inkling.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That next morning when my dad came to the house, he-- this SS Montek said to him, you're free to go now, if you choose.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the words were to him, he says, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I hope that you will be able, in essence, survive the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My father chose to-- at that point, not to go back to camp from the house, which was probably maybe half a mile.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he just went into the woods, and started walking back towards this Polish village, Palikrowy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in the year of 19-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] early '43.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no blankets and pillows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was just the wooden platform, some straw on a platform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You slept almost literally in your clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just staying close to one another.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, there wasn't a separate bunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was just straight platform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody just laid on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
